title: Ep 50: Jenny Pentland Returns! Are Soulmates Real?
description: At last, my beloved friend returns to That's Deep Bro. She skypes in from Hawaii and we discuss soulmates amongst many other totally deep topics. It's a cosmic ride you will love.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
